GLOBAL VIEW CO said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 42.55% to NT$6,972,000 from NT$12,136,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales             6,972            12,136    
YOY%             -42.55%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales             28,516           54,580    
YOY%             -47.75% 
=================================================================
 